OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777406752
OL,3,CJersey shoe fitter on poorly fitted
OL,4,Cshoes leaving children with foot
OL,5,Cdeformities
OL,7,FA Jersey shoe shop owner says she is
OL,8,Fseeing children with "bunions, burns,
OL,9,Fand ingrown toenails" after wearing
OL,10,Fshoes that are the incorrect size.
OL,12,FShoe fitter Audrey Laurens-Chalmers
OL,13,Fhas joined a national campaign
OL,14,Fhighlighting the consequences of
OL,15,Fpoorly fitted shoes.
OL,17,F"Bunions on four-year-olds, starting
OL,18,Fto form because of bad-fitting
OL,19,Ffootwear," she told ITV News.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777406752
OL,3,CJersey shoe fitter on poorly fitted
OL,4,Cshoes leaving children with foot
OL,5,Cdeformities
OL,7,F"Children can trip if their shoes are
OL,8,Ftoo small; they can't open their toes
OL,9,Ffor balance - that's what I'm seeing
OL,10,Fmore of."
OL,12,FHowever, there are concerns from
OL,13,Fparents that recommended shoes come at
OL,14,Fa cost that they "can't physically
OL,15,Fafford".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777406752
OL,3,CJersey shoe fitter on poorly fitted
OL,4,Cshoes leaving children with foot
OL,5,Cdeformities
OL,7,FAudrey says: "Unfortunately, because
OL,8,Fthe bones in their children's feet are
OL,9,Fstill soft, you can change the shape
OL,10,Fof their feet, and once you have done
OL,11,Fit, that could be it - you would be
OL,12,Fresponsible for your child having lots
OL,13,Fof foot problems when they get older.
OL,15,F"Nowadays, lots of people are buying
OL,16,Foff the shelf and online, and the
OL,17,Freasons I get given are that sometimes
OL,18,Fit's the cost, but it depends on what
OL,19,Fprice you put your childs foothealth.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777406752
OL,3,CJersey shoe fitter on poorly fitted
OL,4,Cshoes leaving children with foot
OL,5,Cdeformities
OL,7,F"Also, convenience, sometimes they
OL,8,Fdon't want to bother coming into a
OL,9,Fshop and getting it properly done when
OL,10,Fthey can click and buy something
OL,11,Fonline.
OL,13,F"It is not just tiny children, I am
OL,14,Fseeing it with the older ones as well,
OL,15,Fbecause your feet don't stop growing
OL,16,Funtil you're in your mid-teens."
OL,18,F"I am seeing bunions, I am seeing
OL,19,Fburns, rubs, in grown toenails, all
OL,20,Fthat sort of thing, completely as a
OL,21,Fresult of poor-fitting footwear."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777406752
OL,3,CJersey shoe fitter on poorly fitted
OL,4,Cshoes leaving children with foot
OL,5,Cdeformities
OL,7,FHow often should parents measure their
OL,8,Fchildren's feet?
OL,10,FAccording to the campaign group, The
OL,11,FFootwear Hub, children under two years
OL,12,Fold should have their feet measured
OL,13,Fand checked by a specialist every six
OL,14,Fto eight weeks.
OL,16,FChildren two or older should have
OL,17,Ftheir feet measured and fit-checked
OL,18,Fevery eight to 12 weeks.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777406752
OL,3,CJersey shoe fitter on poorly fitted
OL,4,Cshoes leaving children with foot
OL,5,Cdeformities
OL,7,FWhilst shoe fittings are free, a
OL,8,FJersey mother of three, Samathana
OL,9,FGoguelin, says it is the shoes that
OL,10,Fare too expensive: "It is a struggle,
OL,11,Fa complete struggle.
OL,13,F"With the cost of living, the rents,
OL,14,Fyou live day by day - even with going
OL,15,Fto charities to help you, that is a
OL,16,Fstruggle.
OL,18,F"Especially if you have more than one
OL,19,Fchild, you can't physically afford #40
OL,20,Fon one pair of shoes.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777406752
OL,3,CJersey shoe fitter on poorly fitted
OL,4,Cshoes leaving children with foot
OL,5,Cdeformities
OL,7,F"I don't think people should buy
OL,8,Fexpensive shoes because, for younger
OL,9,Fchildren, they just get wrecked
OL,10,Fstraight away."
OL,12,FSamantha says parents having to buy
OL,13,Fmultiple new shoes is "100% not
OL,14,Frealistic."
OL,16,FNicole Charman, a podiatrist in
OL,17,FJersey, says there are consequences
OL,18,Ffor children having ill-fitted shoes.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777406752
OL,3,CJersey shoe fitter on poorly fitted
OL,4,Cshoes leaving children with foot
OL,5,Cdeformities
OL,7,FShe explains: "The most crucial
OL,8,Fdevelopment period is from the moment
OL,9,Fthey are born through to when they are
OL,10,Fthree years old, so at that point in
OL,11,Ftheir life, their feet are very
OL,12,Fmalleable: it's just soft tissue and
OL,13,Fcartilage.
OL,15,F"So if you were to stick a small
OL,16,Fbaby's foot into a shoe that's not
OL,17,Fcorrectly fitting, it could have long-
OL,18,Fterm effects.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777406752
OL,3,CJersey shoe fitter on poorly fitted
OL,4,Cshoes leaving children with foot
OL,5,Cdeformities
OL,7,F"Minor consequences might be things
OL,8,Fsuch as blisters, corns, calluses -
OL,9,Funcomfortable but not life-altering.
OL,11,F"More major problems you see in
OL,12,Fchildren due to tight-fitting footwear
OL,13,Fcan be chronic, painful ingrown
OL,14,Ftoenails, and foot and ankle pain.
OL,15,FSome children have something called
OL,16,FSever's disease, which is inflammation
OL,17,Fof the growth plates in their heels.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777406752
OL,3,CJersey shoe fitter on poorly fitted
OL,4,Cshoes leaving children with foot
OL,5,Cdeformities
OL,7,F"With Sever's disease, it's not to do
OL,8,Fwith footwear as such, but it tends to
OL,9,Fbe in very sporty children, doing
OL,10,Frunning, jumping sort of activities,
OL,11,Fbut ill-fitting footwear, or footwear
OL,12,Fnot supportive enough, can definitely
OL,13,Fcontribute to Sever's disease."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/10
